1
00:00:00,006 --> 00:01:00,006
( Watch on www.kissasia.co, .club, .be, .org, .net, .id, .xyz )

2
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:34,200
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:35,359
Boss!

4
00:01:35,359 --> 00:01:36,359
Boss, are you okay?

5
00:01:36,359 --> 00:01:37,480
Are you okay?

6
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,920
Are you hurt, Boss?

7
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:41,239
Boss, why is blood gushing out of your hand?

8
00:01:41,239 --> 00:01:43,159
It's nothing.

9
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:46,679
Why is everyone barking away?

10
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,200
How's your hand?

11
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,560
Boss, you've lost so much blood.

12
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:53,959
Hao!

13
00:01:53,959 --> 00:01:55,000
Who's Hao?

14
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,040
Hao, are you okay?

15
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,280
Seems like that was Liu Yi's original name.

16
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,480
Sis! Sis!

17
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,560
- Hao!
- I'm fine.

18
00:02:02,359 --> 00:02:04,760
What are you doing?

19
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,400
Get lost!

20
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:08,200
Step aside, all of you!

21
00:02:09,919 --> 00:02:11,279
Move!

22
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:13,160
Sis!

23
00:02:17,319 --> 00:02:18,479
Back off!

24
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:21,879
No one is allowed to bully him!

25
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:24,199
Back off!

26
00:02:24,199 --> 00:02:26,159
Sis!

27
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:27,880
Go!

28
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:28,919
Back!

29
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:30,999
Step back, everyone!

30
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,719
He's just a kid! Stay away!

31
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:36,640
No one is allowed to bully Hao!

32
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:39,880
Hao!

33
00:02:43,280 --> 00:02:45,080
Hao!

34
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:47,280
Hao, are you okay?

35
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:49,719
Did they hurt you, Hao?

36
00:02:49,719 --> 00:02:51,760
Hao, are you okay?

37
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:53,639
It's all because of me.

38
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:54,840
It's all my fault.

39
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,039
- Sis!
- It's all my fault.

40
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:57,599
- Sis!
- It's my responsibility.

41
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:59,080
I didn't protect you properly.

42
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,279
Sis!

43
00:03:01,719 --> 00:03:03,320
I'm Hao.

44
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,839
See?

45
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,040
I'm fine now.

46
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:25,119
You're perfectly fine.

47
00:03:26,599 --> 00:03:28,600
You're fine.

48
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,280
You're fine.

49
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,439
You're alive and well.

50
00:03:40,679 --> 00:03:41,719
You're fine.

51
00:03:41,719 --> 00:03:44,800
Sis, I'll take you home.

52
00:03:46,879 --> 00:03:49,039
Home.

53
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:50,920
You're fine.

54
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,800
- Let's go.
- Hao...

55
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,519
- Come on.
- Hao...

56
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,399
Stop looking.

57
00:04:08,639 --> 00:04:10,320
My backpack!

58
00:04:48,279 --> 00:04:49,600
Isn't that Dual Blades Xia?

59
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,480
Who's that next to him?

60
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,480
Doesn't look like a gangster.

61
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:56,040
What are you trying to do?

62
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,680
What are you doing?

63
00:04:57,680 --> 00:05:00,560
If a single hair on my sister
is touched, you're dead.

64
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:04,399
Can we take the alley?

65
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:05,879
What are you afraid of?

66
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:07,720
I'm here.

67
00:05:08,959 --> 00:05:12,519
I'm just afraid Dad
will see me with gang members.

68
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:14,160
He'll worry about me.

69
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:19,160
I, Dual Blades Xia, have nothing to fear.

70
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:21,959
There's no need to be afraid, okay?

71
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:25,240
I should at least have this bit of aura.

72
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:27,439
That's not what I meant.

73
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:31,639
Fine, take the alley!

74
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:34,879
Move aside.

75
00:05:43,327 --> 00:05:44,887
[Loyalty]

76
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:48,439
How's your sister now?

77
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,600
She's asleep.

78
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,720
You can take a look yourself.

79
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,800
Okay.

80
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:14,480
Step over the ancestral hall gate.

81
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,560
The brave soul lives and dies.

82
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,759
Loyalty and righteousness
engraved in the heart.

83
00:06:18,759 --> 00:06:20,720
Two slashes mark the traitor.

84
00:06:31,959 --> 00:06:33,559
Why won't you come in?

85
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:37,840
I won't join the gang.

86
00:06:43,199 --> 00:06:46,559
Today, you've seen
all the secrets of Xiaoqi Hall.

87
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:48,999
If you don't step over,

88
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:54,800
then I'll have no choice
but to cut you down.

89
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,519
You won't kill me.

90
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:09,639
You just saved me.

91
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:11,840
If you kill me,
it'll be a waste of your effort.

92
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:13,839
And I don't think you're the kind of person

93
00:07:13,839 --> 00:07:16,319
who just slashes and kills recklessly.

94
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:17,319
You're from Xiaoqi Hall,

95
00:07:17,319 --> 00:07:19,480
the mighty Dual Blades Xia,

96
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,560
destined for great things.

97
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:24,679
I'm just a university student with no weapons.

98
00:07:25,519 --> 00:07:27,520
Why would I be worthy of tainting your blades?

99
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,280
I really didn't expect this.

100
00:07:43,319 --> 00:07:45,920
You really know how to flatter people, huh?

101
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:51,680
Four eyes, you want to be my lackey?

102
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,319
I wouldn't even want you.

103
00:07:54,839 --> 00:07:57,279
Who wants to be your lackey?

104
00:07:57,279 --> 00:07:59,639
No one does.

105
00:07:59,639 --> 00:08:00,999
Bandage me.

106
00:08:03,079 --> 00:08:04,439
All right.

107
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:10,680
It might hurt a bit.

108
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,800
Just bear with it.

109
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,400
Who do you think I am?

110
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:18,280
Since I was little,

111
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:19,480
I've had more injuries
than the books you've read.

112
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,800
What's this small injury compared to that?

113
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:26,559
He Chu San, why are you pressing so hard?

114
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,480
I'm not.

115
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,040
Don't pretend.

116
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,080
I've always thought you were dishonest.

117
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:36,279
You've been messing with me
ever since you started writing the script.

118
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:37,780
And then you went to complain to my sis.

119
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:39,600
I could tell right away
you're not a good person.

120
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,879
Don't think I'm clueless.

121
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:42,880
I just didn't feel like arguing with you.

122
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,040
Well, you must be the bigger person.

123
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:50,679
You're so smooth with your words.

124
00:08:52,894 --> 00:08:55,199
- Xia Liu Yi.
- It's "Big Bro" for you.

125
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,319
Big Bro Liu Yi.

126
00:08:59,639 --> 00:09:01,480
You have an injury on your face, too.

127
00:09:01,480 --> 00:09:03,559
Come here, I'll tend to it for you.

128
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:27,240
By the way, that day backstage,

129
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,880
what did Xiao Man ask you?

130
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:34,479
She asked me what love is.

131
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,720
How did you answer her?

132
00:09:38,720 --> 00:09:41,040
I didn't get a chance to answer her.

133
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:46,200
Actually, I don't know either.

134
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:48,839
This is the first time
I've written a love story.

135
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,280
You wrote it terribly.

136
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,920
But the book did say...

137
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,280
Love...

138
00:10:05,559 --> 00:10:08,720
is when a person is willing to risk everything

139
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:11,559
to save someone else.

140
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:26,359
Big Bro Liu Yi.

141
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:29,120
Why did you save me?

142
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,599
He Chu San.

143
00:10:36,039 --> 00:10:37,559
You really are...

144
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:51,479
so noisy.

145
00:11:00,601 --> 00:11:05,074
[Become A Love Expert in Three Days]
[Love Story Encyclopedia]

146
00:11:05,074 --> 00:11:07,042
[Romantic Language]

147
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,640
San.

148
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:27,480
San! You're back!

149
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:30,200
You didn't come home all night yesterday.

150
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,120
You didn't even go to Fei's place.

151
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:35,480
What happened to your head?

152
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,519
Tell me.

153
00:11:36,519 --> 00:11:38,360
Did someone bully you outside?

154
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,559
No.

155
00:11:39,559 --> 00:11:41,480
Dad, please tell Fei

156
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:44,279
I won't be going to work these two weeks.

157
00:11:44,279 --> 00:11:48,559
I've recently joined a new project development.

158
00:11:48,559 --> 00:11:49,880
I'm really busy.

159
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:54,240
Then you were at school yesterday, right?

160
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,760
What about your head?

161
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,760
A little black dog bit it.

162
00:11:59,639 --> 00:12:00,920
It's fine.

163
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:04,479
By the way, Dad.

164
00:12:05,519 --> 00:12:06,759
I want to ask you something.

165
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:09,559
If someone easily gets frightened

166
00:12:09,559 --> 00:12:11,480
and then loses their mind,

167
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:15,120
what's a good way to treat them?

168
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,400
Student, you're so energetic today.

169
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:36,759
Xiao Ma, aren't we filming today?

170
00:12:36,759 --> 00:12:38,559
Big Sis is sick, so she's resting today.

171
00:12:38,559 --> 00:12:40,000
What about the little black dog?

172
00:12:41,679 --> 00:12:43,319
What about Big Bro Liu Yi?

173
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:50,319
Who do you think you are?

174
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:53,480
Why would Boss need to tell you anything?

175
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:54,760
Four eyes!

176
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,480
Come here.

177
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:04,240
Then please help me to pass this to Big Sis.

178
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,480
This is the calming powder Dad prescribed.

179
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:09,520
And this is the answer Big Sis wanted.

180
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:17,480
Do you think just because
you've been out with Boss a few times,

181
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:19,120
you've risen in status?

182
00:13:20,159 --> 00:13:21,720
Don't you know who Big Sis is?

183
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:24,400
Do you think she can take
medicine given by anyone?

184
00:13:25,039 --> 00:13:27,079
You're just a useless guy.

185
00:13:32,519 --> 00:13:36,400
Big Sis asked you to deliver it personally?

186
00:13:40,519 --> 00:13:41,960
Give me the money.

187
00:13:41,960 --> 00:13:43,920
I'm in a good mood today.

188
00:13:44,799 --> 00:13:46,079
You're in luck today.

189
00:13:47,919 --> 00:13:49,400
Thank you, Xiao Ma.

190
00:13:52,480 --> 00:13:54,280
Go do your thing.

191
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,800
Hurry up.

192
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:00,240
- Deal the cards.
- Continue.

193
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:02,920
Money, give me the money.

194
00:14:22,039 --> 00:14:23,080
A love letter.

195
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,120
Love?

196
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,080
Boss.

197
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:36,159
Just now, that student

198
00:14:36,159 --> 00:14:38,759
asked me to deliver a letter to Big Sis.

199
00:14:38,759 --> 00:14:40,400
The lead guy said

200
00:14:41,519 --> 00:14:42,879
it's a love letter.

201
00:14:42,879 --> 00:14:44,200
What nonsense are you talking about?

202
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,319
Get lost.

203
00:15:13,559 --> 00:15:14,839
Sis.

204
00:15:16,039 --> 00:15:17,519
It's me.

205
00:15:17,519 --> 00:15:18,800
Liu Yi.

206
00:15:25,039 --> 00:15:26,960
Liu Yi.

207
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:28,719
You're here.

208
00:15:32,039 --> 00:15:33,639
I've taken over a few shops recently.

209
00:15:33,639 --> 00:15:36,000
The boss of Guan Shan Song
gave me a bunch of stuff.

210
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,280
Do you like it?

211
00:15:40,519 --> 00:15:42,279
What's wrong?

212
00:15:42,279 --> 00:15:44,920
Why didn't you stay at the ancestral hall
for a few more days?

213
00:15:46,879 --> 00:15:49,240
None of you are there.

214
00:15:49,240 --> 00:15:52,079
I don't want to stay there alone.

215
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,480
Where's Big Bro?

216
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:56,120
Isn't he with you?

217
00:15:59,679 --> 00:16:02,919
He only shows up occasionally.

218
00:16:02,919 --> 00:16:05,040
And then disappears for a long time.

219
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:09,839
- He...
- Like a seagull.

220
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:13,760
He's very busy.

221
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,679
What about you?

222
00:16:21,000 --> 00:16:22,920
You're busy, too.

223
00:16:24,559 --> 00:16:26,880
You never come to see me.

224
00:16:27,639 --> 00:16:32,399
Do you think I'm sick and can't recognize you?

225
00:16:32,399 --> 00:16:34,320
- No.
- It's not that.

226
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:35,879
I don't mean to.

227
00:16:35,879 --> 00:16:39,319
I... I don't know what happened.

228
00:16:40,039 --> 00:16:41,639
You were frightened at that time.

229
00:16:41,639 --> 00:16:43,319
It wasn't your fault.

230
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:51,160
Madam, it's time for your medicine.

231
00:17:07,279 --> 00:17:09,359
I've been following the doctor's orders lately.

232
00:17:09,359 --> 00:17:10,680
Taking my medicine on time.

233
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:13,280
I'll get better soon.

234
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:16,399
You're amazing, Big Sis.

235
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:20,160
Liu Yi, do you know?

236
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:24,599
Actually, I'm not sick.

237
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:29,200
I just get a bit upset sometimes.

238
00:17:31,400 --> 00:17:33,279
I'm upset.

239
00:17:33,279 --> 00:17:36,240
Why do I have to take medicine so often?

240
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:37,680
I get upset.

241
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:41,079
Why is it so easy for me to feel upset?

242
00:17:41,079 --> 00:17:43,920
I'm upset that he never comes to see me.

243
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:45,800
I'm upset...

244
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:51,280
What's wrong?

245
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:55,280
He doesn't love me.

246
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:01,519
Doesn't love you?

247
00:18:01,519 --> 00:18:02,919
How could that be?

248
00:18:09,759 --> 00:18:12,599
Cheng Qing, you don't love me.

249
00:18:12,599 --> 00:18:13,599
I'm Liu Yi.

250
00:18:13,599 --> 00:18:14,839
Big Sis?

251
00:18:16,519 --> 00:18:17,839
Cheng Qing.

252
00:18:17,839 --> 00:18:20,359
You love me.

253
00:18:20,359 --> 00:18:23,800
Then why do you rarely hug me?

254
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:30,159
When you hug me, I've looked at you seriously.

255
00:18:32,319 --> 00:18:35,200
Your soul isn't here.

256
00:18:36,519 --> 00:18:38,480
Your eyes...

257
00:18:39,519 --> 00:18:43,640
They seem to be looking at someone far away.

258
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:45,960
You don't love me.

259
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,640
Where is your soul?

260
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:49,799
- Big Sis.
- Your soul has flown away.

261
00:18:49,799 --> 00:18:50,920
Like that seagull.

262
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,400
I'm Liu Yi.

263
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:55,279
- Big Sis.
- You don't love me.

264
00:18:55,279 --> 00:18:57,279
If you don't love me,
then why did you marry me?

265
00:18:57,279 --> 00:18:59,160
- Big Sis.
- Why?

266
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:01,559
Who is it that you really love?

267
00:19:01,559 --> 00:19:03,160
Big Sis.

268
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,640
Big Sis, it's me.

269
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:06,280
I'm Liu Yi.

270
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,880
I'm Liu Yi. It's me.

271
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:16,159
I'm Liu Yi.

272
00:19:19,640 --> 00:19:20,960
It's okay now.

273
00:19:23,759 --> 00:19:25,480
L-Liu Yi.

274
00:19:28,359 --> 00:19:29,480
I...

275
00:19:30,160 --> 00:19:33,079
I...

276
00:19:33,079 --> 00:19:35,159
- Was I just...
- It's okay now.

277
00:19:35,799 --> 00:19:37,480
It's really okay now.

278
00:20:09,359 --> 00:20:12,200
Cheng Qing, you don't love me.

279
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,119
Your eyes...

280
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:18,720
They seem to be looking at someone far away.

281
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:21,839
Boss, Liu Yi's waiting for you.

282
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:27,720
Why are you here?

283
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,639
I heard you got hurt.

284
00:20:41,599 --> 00:20:43,200
Why don't you stay here tonight?

285
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:44,599
You can sleep in the guest room.

286
00:20:53,799 --> 00:20:55,000
Brother.

287
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:59,279
Do you have someone else on the side?

288
00:20:59,279 --> 00:21:01,280
What nonsense are you talking about?

289
00:21:03,039 --> 00:21:05,319
Big Sis said you don't love her.

290
00:21:05,319 --> 00:21:07,319
She said there's someone else in your heart.

291
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:16,040
Do you still remember

292
00:21:17,079 --> 00:21:19,319
what you said when you...

293
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,359
begged me to marry Xiao Man?

294
00:21:32,160 --> 00:21:33,720
You're about to turn twenty.

295
00:21:33,720 --> 00:21:35,880
What birthday gift do you want?

296
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,599
Will you agree to anything I want?

297
00:21:37,599 --> 00:21:38,799
Of course.

298
00:21:38,799 --> 00:21:40,680
I care about you so much.

299
00:21:43,079 --> 00:21:44,800
I want...

300
00:21:46,519 --> 00:21:48,480
my sister to be your wife.

301
00:21:53,079 --> 00:21:54,480
You said...

302
00:21:56,039 --> 00:21:58,159
you hope the three of us

303
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:01,480
can be like a real family.

304
00:22:01,480 --> 00:22:03,440
Forever together.

305
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,960
I agreed.

306
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,800
That's because...

307
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:14,119
I wish the same.

308
00:22:14,119 --> 00:22:17,839
And I only hope for that.

309
00:22:19,799 --> 00:22:22,200
So, don't say such nonsense anymore.

310
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:34,280
There's a nice Western restaurant
near Repulse Bay.

311
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:37,000
I'll take her there in a few days.

312
00:22:40,200 --> 00:22:41,879
Brother.

313
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,599
Brother!

314
00:22:53,799 --> 00:22:56,040
Can't you love her truly?

315
00:23:14,119 --> 00:23:16,119
Your tie looks good today.

316
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:43,680
It's been a week.

317
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:45,960
A whole week without filming.

318
00:23:45,960 --> 00:23:48,119
Liu Yi hasn't shown up either.

319
00:23:48,119 --> 00:23:51,559
I don't know when
I can return to school for classes.

320
00:23:51,559 --> 00:23:53,079
If I don't go back soon,

321
00:23:53,079 --> 00:23:55,280
the school will probably expel me.

322
00:24:04,279 --> 00:24:06,359
Liu Yi, you're here.

323
00:24:08,359 --> 00:24:10,639
Liu Yi, you play billiards really well.

324
00:24:12,319 --> 00:24:13,800
Watch carefully.

325
00:24:22,480 --> 00:24:24,000
Okay.

326
00:24:29,839 --> 00:24:31,200
How is it?

327
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:35,280
How is it?

328
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:39,559
How's your injury?

329
00:24:39,559 --> 00:24:40,799
Are you blind?

330
00:24:40,799 --> 00:24:41,960
All nonsense.

331
00:24:41,960 --> 00:24:44,359
What about your sister?

332
00:24:46,839 --> 00:24:48,639
What exactly are you trying to say?

333
00:24:50,279 --> 00:24:52,960
Dad got me a new doctor...

334
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:56,519
No, my dad got me a new calming prescription,

335
00:24:56,519 --> 00:24:59,400
and a blood-activating,
bruise-healing medicine.

336
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:01,359
For you and Big Sis.

337
00:25:01,359 --> 00:25:04,280
I don't know if it will be useful.

338
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:16,519
I suspected you had a problem before.

339
00:25:16,519 --> 00:25:18,200
- Did you have feelings for my sister?
- No.

340
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:19,880
Then why are you so nice to my sister?

341
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,000
I heard that when I wasn't around,

342
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:23,200
you asked around about my sister.

343
00:25:24,519 --> 00:25:27,680
I was just worried about you two.

344
00:25:28,599 --> 00:25:30,159
Liu Yi.

345
00:25:31,279 --> 00:25:33,319
Are you bullying Chu San again?

346
00:25:33,319 --> 00:25:34,680
No.

347
00:25:34,680 --> 00:25:36,079
Definitely not.

348
00:25:36,839 --> 00:25:38,640
Chu San, are you okay?

349
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:40,879
Just my ear feels a bit...

350
00:25:41,799 --> 00:25:44,000
My ear is a bit thick.

351
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:45,599
It doesn't hurt.

352
00:25:45,599 --> 00:25:46,960
Yes, Sis.

353
00:25:46,960 --> 00:25:48,519
I was just teasing him.

354
00:25:48,519 --> 00:25:49,920
Right?

355
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:51,680
Right, Chu San?

356
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:54,839
What's this?

357
00:25:56,200 --> 00:25:57,960
These are for Big Sis.

358
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,960
Supplements. Tonic supplements.

359
00:26:00,720 --> 00:26:04,240
Sis, you look really pretty today.

360
00:26:04,240 --> 00:26:06,119
- Really?
- Yes.

361
00:26:06,920 --> 00:26:10,799
Cheng Qing is taking me
to a Western restaurant for steak.

362
00:26:10,799 --> 00:26:12,839
Their steaks are really delicious.

363
00:26:12,839 --> 00:26:15,280
Chu San, do you like steak?

364
00:26:17,079 --> 00:26:18,520
I've never had it.

365
00:26:19,559 --> 00:26:20,880
Western food is too expensive.

366
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:25,639
One meal would cost me
a month's living expenses.

367
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:29,480
Then why don't you come with us?

368
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:30,720
Cheng Qing will pay.

369
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:32,359
As a reward for your letter.

370
00:26:34,720 --> 00:26:35,960
No way.

371
00:26:36,759 --> 00:26:38,920
Liu Yi, you should be more generous.

372
00:26:38,920 --> 00:26:42,079
No, it's not about generosity.

373
00:26:45,959 --> 00:26:47,000
Come with us.

374
00:26:47,000 --> 00:26:48,680
It's not like there's no room.

375
00:26:50,160 --> 00:26:51,200
Let's go.

376
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:53,079
Come on.

377
00:27:06,400 --> 00:27:08,760
It's not like I wanted to go.

378
00:27:16,839 --> 00:27:18,280
Let's go.

379
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:26,960
Hope to see you again.

380
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:33,839
Good evening, Mr. Hao.

381
00:27:33,839 --> 00:27:35,839
You reserved a Christmas-themed table for two.

382
00:27:35,839 --> 00:27:38,280
Do you want to change it to four people now?

383
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:42,279
We'll sit over there.

384
00:27:42,279 --> 00:27:45,599
You two can sit over there.

385
00:27:45,599 --> 00:27:48,319
Okay, it's rare for you
to make friends on your own.

386
00:27:48,319 --> 00:27:50,200
Take care of Chu San.

387
00:27:50,200 --> 00:27:52,159
- I will.
- This way.

388
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:54,760
We'll go over there.

389
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:31,639
Say, don't they make a perfect pair?

390
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,599
Don't you know how to eat?

391
00:28:37,599 --> 00:28:39,599
Then use your hands.

392
00:28:44,839 --> 00:28:46,000
Excuse me!

393
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:48,480
A pair of chopsticks, please.

394
00:28:48,480 --> 00:28:50,039
Sir, this is a Western restaurant.

395
00:28:50,039 --> 00:28:52,599
No one eats Western food with chopsticks.

396
00:28:52,599 --> 00:28:53,680
Chopsticks.

397
00:28:53,680 --> 00:28:54,680
Do you understand?

398
00:28:54,680 --> 00:28:57,079
We Chinese use chopsticks when we eat.

399
00:28:57,079 --> 00:28:59,119
All right, please wait a moment.

400
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:03,440
He sure talks a lot.

401
00:29:07,559 --> 00:29:10,839
Thank you, Xia Liu Yi.

402
00:29:15,720 --> 00:29:17,919
Also, thanks for saving me that day.

403
00:29:25,519 --> 00:29:27,839
Don't flatter yourself.

404
00:29:27,839 --> 00:29:29,480
You help me out.

405
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:31,480
That makes you my henchman.

406
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:33,880
Taking care of my brothers
is what a leader should do.

407
00:29:33,880 --> 00:29:35,520
I'm not your henchman.

408
00:29:36,160 --> 00:29:38,039
After you finish writing your script,

409
00:29:38,039 --> 00:29:40,200
we won't have anything to do with each other.

410
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:42,039
Even if you die on the streets,

411
00:29:42,039 --> 00:29:43,919
I won't even glance at you.

412
00:29:46,599 --> 00:29:48,319
Sir, your chopsticks.

413
00:29:55,759 --> 00:29:57,480
Gangster. Rogue.

414
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:59,000
Beast in human clothes.
Man with an animal's heart.

415
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,440
Cold and ruthless.

416
00:30:04,359 --> 00:30:06,751
He Chu San!

417
00:30:06,751 --> 00:30:08,839
Three second rule! It's still edible!

418
00:30:17,559 --> 00:30:20,919
Cheng Qing, this place looks great.

419
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:23,279
Do you remember?

420
00:30:23,279 --> 00:30:26,200
Actually, you've brought me here before.

421
00:30:26,200 --> 00:30:28,759
Back then, we spent Christmas together.

422
00:30:28,759 --> 00:30:30,799
We had a barbecue nearby.

423
00:30:30,799 --> 00:30:32,400
We even set off fireworks.

424
00:30:32,400 --> 00:30:34,119
Liu Yi was especially mischievous.

425
00:30:34,119 --> 00:30:36,000
He got his butt burned by a firework.

426
00:30:42,720 --> 00:30:44,240
I won't bring you along next time.

427
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,439
Sorry.

428
00:30:45,439 --> 00:30:46,440
It got on my clothes.

429
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:47,799
These clothes are expensive.

430
00:30:47,799 --> 00:30:49,160
Then I'll help you wash it.

431
00:30:49,160 --> 00:30:50,640
Sorry about that.

432
00:30:50,640 --> 00:30:52,960
Liu Yi is still as mischievous as ever.

433
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:55,319
Yes.

434
00:30:55,319 --> 00:30:59,000
Liu Yi is becoming more like
a little troublemaker.

435
00:31:02,407 --> 00:31:04,498
Cheng Qing.

436
00:31:05,910 --> 00:31:08,166
Am I boring you?

437
00:31:09,079 --> 00:31:10,720
Not at all.

438
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:12,520
Why would you think that?

439
00:31:14,839 --> 00:31:17,000
Is the steak not to your taste?

440
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:18,520
Try mine.

441
00:31:33,599 --> 00:31:35,079
Cheng Qing.

442
00:31:37,559 --> 00:31:39,200
Let's get a divorce.

443
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:45,559
Are you feeling unwell?

444
00:31:45,559 --> 00:31:47,040
Did you bring any medicine?

445
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:54,119
No.

446
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:59,599
I'm completely clear-headed and calm.

447
00:32:00,839 --> 00:32:02,036
You...

448
00:32:02,036 --> 00:32:03,760
You don't love me.

449
00:32:10,279 --> 00:32:12,040
Our marriage...

450
00:32:13,839 --> 00:32:16,720
If it's only been my one-sided wish,

451
00:32:18,119 --> 00:32:20,159
then it's all a mistake.

452
00:32:25,240 --> 00:32:27,480
- Xiao Man...
- I've known for a long time.

453
00:32:28,559 --> 00:32:31,079
I just didn't want to admit it.

454
00:32:31,960 --> 00:32:35,119
I thought... I loved you.

455
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:38,639
And you've always treated me so well.

456
00:32:41,759 --> 00:32:44,480
We'd definitely be happy.

457
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:48,159
But I was wrong.

458
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:52,760
Love isn't in the eyes.

459
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:56,399
It's in the heart.

460
00:33:13,319 --> 00:33:17,040
You treat me well because of family affection.

461
00:33:20,279 --> 00:33:22,200
But what I want...

462
00:33:26,119 --> 00:33:28,359
What I want is love.

463
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:30,280
I'm sorry.

464
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:36,480
You don't have to admit it so quickly.

465
00:33:38,079 --> 00:33:39,839
Just lie to me for a moment.

466
00:33:41,160 --> 00:33:42,800
Not even that?

467
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:48,040
I'm sorry.

468
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:53,440
You... You don't have to say sorry.

469
00:33:55,480 --> 00:33:56,359
Wasn't it the same back then?

470
00:33:56,359 --> 00:33:58,951
I didn't ask about your feelings

471
00:33:58,951 --> 00:34:02,280
and just dragged both of us
all the way to this point.

472
00:34:06,279 --> 00:34:08,200
Liu Yi wouldn't agree.

473
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,479
Liu Yi...

474
00:34:23,119 --> 00:34:25,640
He's just too worried about me.

475
00:34:30,599 --> 00:34:32,319
All along...

476
00:34:33,880 --> 00:34:36,080
Even though I'm the older sister,

477
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:42,999
he's been the one trying to protect me,

478
00:34:44,559 --> 00:34:46,999
and giving me everything I need.

479
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:54,359
Let's wait until the movie is over.

480
00:34:59,239 --> 00:35:01,120
After the movie wraps up,

481
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:04,760
I'll tell him.

482
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:09,120
I'll say it with you.

483
00:35:15,679 --> 00:35:17,200
Cheng Qing.

484
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:19,280
Can you...

485
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:25,519
tell me who you really like?

486
00:35:30,039 --> 00:35:31,479
I'm sorry.

487
00:35:38,320 --> 00:35:39,760
Hao Cheng Qing.

488
00:35:41,239 --> 00:35:43,160
You're such an idiot.

489
00:36:02,920 --> 00:36:04,800
Okay, okay, no rush.

490
00:36:04,800 --> 00:36:07,920
There's enough for everyone.

491
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:08,960
This one's yours.

492
00:36:08,960 --> 00:36:10,479
Take your time.

493
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:12,440
Thank you.

494
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:13,960
Come back for more.

495
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:15,840
Thanks. What kind of event is this?

496
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:17,760
- It's so lively.
- A new movie is showing.

497
00:36:17,760 --> 00:36:19,280
I heard it's pretty good.

498
00:36:19,280 --> 00:36:21,280
- Is that right?
- Come and see for yourself.

499
00:36:22,519 --> 00:36:26,000
"Heroes of the Streets."

500
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:28,560
Starring Xia Xiao Man.

501
00:36:29,855 --> 00:36:32,199
[Producer: Xia Liu Yi]
[Screenplay: He Chu San]

502
00:36:32,199 --> 00:36:33,320
Do you want to watch it?

503
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:34,680
No.

504
00:36:35,519 --> 00:36:37,280
You should watch it with your dad.

505
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:38,400
It'll be fun.

506
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:41,800
Look. Producer, Xia Liu Yi.

507
00:36:42,719 --> 00:36:43,959
Fei.

508
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:48,119
Dad loves Cantonese opera.

509
00:36:48,119 --> 00:36:50,079
He's not into trendy stuff.

510
00:36:50,079 --> 00:36:53,760
I heard there'll be a performance
at the Chengzhai City God Temple tonight.

511
00:36:53,760 --> 00:36:55,840
It's "The Return of the Red Plum."

512
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:58,960
If Dad knew, he'd definitely be very happy.

513
00:36:58,960 --> 00:36:59,960
- Really?
- Yes.

514
00:36:59,960 --> 00:37:01,119
Will I have time to change my clothes?

515
00:37:01,119 --> 00:37:02,679
Plenty of time. Seven o'clock tonight.

516
00:37:02,679 --> 00:37:03,920
- Really?
- Yes.

517
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:07,239
But this person is really beautiful.

518
00:37:07,239 --> 00:37:08,599
- Let's go.
- Boss, look.

519
00:37:08,599 --> 00:37:10,639
So many flower baskets.

520
00:37:10,639 --> 00:37:12,159
Boss.

521
00:37:12,159 --> 00:37:14,480
Half of the city's influential people are here

522
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:16,120
for this special preview.

523
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:17,880
Boss.

524
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:19,320
Are they going to announce you

525
00:37:19,320 --> 00:37:21,480
as the young master of the hall?

526
00:37:21,480 --> 00:37:23,239
Don't talk nonsense here.

527
00:37:23,239 --> 00:37:24,559
Let me tell you.

528
00:37:24,559 --> 00:37:27,920
They have all invested in the movie.

529
00:37:27,920 --> 00:37:30,599
In the end, they're just here
for the box office share.

530
00:37:30,599 --> 00:37:32,039
Of course they're happy to come.

531
00:37:32,039 --> 00:37:33,079
Young master?

532
00:37:33,079 --> 00:37:34,400
Stop talking nonsense.

533
00:37:34,400 --> 00:37:37,159
If I find out you're making this up later,

534
00:37:37,159 --> 00:37:39,800
I'll cut out your tongue.

535
00:37:40,840 --> 00:37:42,880
Then... this movie is about to be released.

536
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:45,719
Big Sis is going to be famous all over town.

537
00:37:45,719 --> 00:37:47,719
Exactly, exactly.

538
00:37:47,719 --> 00:37:49,840
Of course.

539
00:37:49,840 --> 00:37:51,880
My sister will definitely be happy.

540
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:54,560
Big Bro will definitely be happy, too.

541
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,920
It's almost time.

542
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:58,679
I'm going to pick up Big Bro and my sister.

543
00:37:58,679 --> 00:38:00,679
Watch over this place for me.

544
00:38:00,679 --> 00:38:03,039
- Don't worry.
- We got this.

545
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:06,000
Okay, over here.

546
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:08,070
- Come on, come on.
- Take care of the V.I.Ps.

547
00:38:08,070 --> 00:38:11,733
[Heroes of the Streets]
[Premieres Today]

548
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,720
Big Bro.

549
00:38:37,159 --> 00:38:38,439
Big Sis.

550
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,280
Big Bro.

551
00:38:54,159 --> 00:38:55,479
Big Sis.

552
00:39:00,400 --> 00:39:01,800
Big Sis.

553
00:39:01,800 --> 00:39:03,200
Hao.

554
00:39:04,320 --> 00:39:05,960
- Sister.
- Don't come closer.

555
00:39:05,960 --> 00:39:07,519
Come down quickly.

556
00:39:07,519 --> 00:39:09,080
Come down.

557
00:39:09,719 --> 00:39:11,320
Here.

558
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:13,199
Don't scare me.

559
00:39:13,199 --> 00:39:14,920
Big Sis, what's wrong?

560
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:16,399
Come back quickly.

561
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,959
Big Sis!

562
00:39:27,559 --> 00:39:29,359
Big Sis!

563
00:39:36,880 --> 00:39:39,560
Big Sis!

564
00:40:01,559 --> 00:40:02,959
Liu Yi.

565
00:40:06,159 --> 00:40:07,360
Liu Yi.

566
00:40:07,360 --> 00:40:08,640
Brother.

567
00:40:12,039 --> 00:40:14,800
Big Bro!

568
00:40:18,880 --> 00:40:21,120
Are these my Qing Long Dual Blades?

569
00:40:26,320 --> 00:40:28,159
Big Bro.

570
00:40:28,159 --> 00:40:29,600
I'll take you away.

571
00:40:31,519 --> 00:40:32,800
Hold on to me.

572
00:43:17,280 --> 00:43:19,439
Xia Liu Yi.

573
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:22,599
Aren't you supposed to be brave?

574
00:43:22,599 --> 00:43:25,559
Aren't you the twin red staff expert?

575
00:43:25,559 --> 00:43:27,159
If you've got the guts, come out

576
00:43:27,159 --> 00:43:30,840
and carry away
your brother and sister's bodies.

577
00:43:30,840 --> 00:43:36,959
I really want to see if your blades
are faster than my gun.

578
00:43:56,880 --> 00:43:58,439
Fucking hell.

579
00:43:59,159 --> 00:44:00,639
Spread the word.

580
00:44:00,639 --> 00:44:03,079
Xia Liu Yi killed Big Boss Qing Long

581
00:44:03,079 --> 00:44:06,159
and forced his crazy sister
to jump off the building.

582
00:44:06,159 --> 00:44:09,840
The entire Xiaoqi Hall
is mobilized to capture the traitor.

583
00:44:09,840 --> 00:44:11,519
I want him, dead or alive.

584
00:44:11,519 --> 00:44:13,080
Yes.

585
00:44:29,360 --> 00:44:30,760
Don't move.

586
00:44:37,320 --> 00:44:38,959
Stay quiet.

587
00:44:41,880 --> 00:44:44,039
Prepare some hemostatic powder for me.

588
00:44:45,119 --> 00:44:46,760
And some gauze.

589
00:44:47,639 --> 00:44:48,920
Yes.

590
00:44:48,920 --> 00:44:50,560
Xia Liu Yi.

591
00:44:57,700 --> 00:45:01,399
So, it really is you, damn brat.
